{"view":"article","slug":"pyraminx-l4e-v-first","category":"CHS","subcategory":null,"topDir":"CHS","title":{"zh":"金字塔四棱法 (L4E, V先)"},"content":{"zh":"<p><a id=\"_Hlk48940870\"></a><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-l4e-v-first/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-l4e-v-first/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>金字塔四棱法 (L4E, V先)</strong></p><p>平均 = 3.57+0.67+6.46+0.67 =11.37.</p><p><strong><u>V</u></strong></p><p>理解还原3心及所夹的其中2个棱, 并将未还原棱放在FD. 平均 = 3.57.</p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-l4e-v-first/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong><u>L4E</u></strong></p><p>S = R' L R L', H = L R' L' R. <a id=\"_Hlk35258859\"></a>观察线或棒时不考虑黄棱. 理解学习. AUF: 做完公式后红面朝前. 默认概率 = 1/32. 平均 = 226/35 = 6.46.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"6\"><p><a id=\"_Hlk2791528\"></a><strong>纯翻 [3]</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-l4e-v-first/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> 01</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-l4e-v-first/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> 02</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>1/96 <img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-l4e-v-first/zh/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> 03</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>H U' R U R' (8)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"S R U' R' (7)\"><strong>S R U' R' (7)</strong></span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(L' U L R U' R')2 (12)\"><strong>(L' U L R U' R')2 (12)</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"6\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"6\"><p><strong>顶层 [4]</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-l4e-v-first/zh/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> 04</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/